Edit
hashmap = {}
Ye dictionary (hashmap) store karega ki konsa number pehle aaya hai aur uska index kya hai.

Step 2: Start the for loop
Loop nums list ke har element pe chalega.

ğŸ”¹ First Iteration (i = 0, num = 2)
