ğŸ”¹ Second Iteration (i = 1, num = 7)
remain = target - num = 9 - 7 = 2

Check karenge ki 2 hashmap me hai? âœ… (Yes! 2: 0)

Iska matlab nums[0] + nums[1] = 2 + 7 = 9 ho gaya.

return [hashmap[2], 1] â†’ return [0, 1]

Final Output:
python
Copy
Edit
