Step 1: Problem ko chhote parts me divide karo
ğŸ‘‰ Problem Statement: Hume ek list nums[] aur ek target diya hai, hume do numbers ke indices return karne hain jinka sum target ke equal ho.

ğŸ“Œ Example:

