Step 6: Mnemonics ya Memory Tricks use karo
âœ… Hashmap ka simple funda yaad rakho:
â†’ "Pehle store karo, fir check karo"
â†’ Har number ko hashmap me daalo, fir check karo ki remain already hai ya nahi

âœ… Loops yaad rakhne ke liye ek line yaad karo:
â†’ "Ek baar loop chalao, har baar hashmap update karo"

âœ… Interview Trick:
â†’ Jab bhi Two Sum jaisa problem aaye, pehla thought hamesha hashmap hona chahiye!

